LV 2.위장

function solution(clothes) {
    let answer=1;
    let obj={};
    for(let c of clothes){
        if(obj[c[1]]){
            obj[c[1]]++;
        }else{
            obj[c[1]]=1;
        }
    }
    for(let i of Object.keys(obj)){
        answer*=(obj[i]+1);
    }
    console.log(obj.values())

    return answer-1;
}
